{
  "texts": [
    "The model is trained for 1 epoch taking 7 hours on an NVIDIA A100 machine.",
    "For the main paper results, the Llama-2 model is selected due to its best accuracy.",
    "RoBERTa foot_4 is finetuned on the train split of the RACE dataset (RACE-M and RACE-H).",
    "The details of the specific Longformer foot_5 are detailed in Manakul et al. (2023).",
    "For the data complexity classification system, pretrained ELECTRA-base is finetuned on the RACE++ train split with the complexity class (easy, medium or hard) as the label."
  ]
}